thread.title: BRIEF-Tick Trading Software FY Revenue At 5.039 Million Euros, Up 5.5 Pct ​

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Tick Trading Software FY Revenue At 5.039 Million Euros, Up 5.5 Pct ​
text:
Jan 16 (Reuters) - TICK TRADING SOFTWARE AG:
* FY REVENUE 5.039 MILLION EUR (+5.50%)​ * EARNINGS BEFORE TAXES EUR 1.57 MILLION VERSUS EUR 1.89 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FORECAST FISCAL YEAR 2017/2018: NET INCOME FOR THE YEAR 1,250 - 1,500 TEUR
* FORECAST FISCAL YEAR 2018/2019: NET INCOME 1,500 - 1,900 TEUR
* PROPOSES DIVIDEND OF 1.14 EUROS PER SHARE​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
